---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Actualites - APV Valence">

  <section class="px-6 pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="page-subtitle">Informations</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Actualit&eacute;s</h1>
      <p class="body-text">
        Les nouvelles de l&rsquo;Association Philat&eacute;lique de Valence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-5">

      <article class="stamp-card postal-frame paper p-7 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="label">Mars 2026</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">
          <a href="/actualites/fete-du-timbre-2026" class="hover:text-primary-700 transition">F&ecirc;te du Timbre 2026</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-text mb-4">Les 7 et 8 mars 2026, &agrave; la Maison des Associations.</p>
        <a href="/actualites/fete-du-timbre-2026" class="text-[13px] font-medium text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition">Lire l&rsquo;article</a>
      </article>

      <article class="stamp-card postal-frame paper p-7 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="label">Juin 2026</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">
          <a href="/actualites/expophil-2026" class="hover:text-primary-700 transition">Expophil Rh&ocirc;ne-Alpes et centenaire</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-text mb-4">Les 20 et 21 juin 2026, congr&egrave;s r&eacute;gional et centenaire de l&rsquo;APV.</p>
        <a href="/actualites/expophil-2026" class="text-[13px] font-medium text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition">Lire l&rsquo;article</a>
      </article>

      <article class="stamp-card postal-frame paper p-7 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="label">Juin</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">
          <a href="/actualites/paella-21-juin" class="hover:text-primary-700 transition">Paella du 21 juin</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-text mb-4">Moment convivial chez le pr&eacute;sident : paella, discussions et philat&eacute;lie.</p>
        <a href="/actualites/paella-21-juin" class="text-[13px] font-medium text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition">Lire l&rsquo;article</a>
      </article>

      <article class="stamp-card postal-frame paper p-7 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="label">Chaque jeudi</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">
          <a href="/actualites/reunions" class="hover:text-primary-700 transition">R&eacute;unions hebdomadaires</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-text mb-4">Permanences le jeudi apr&egrave;s-midi &agrave; la Maison de la Vie Associative.</p>
        <a href="/actualites/reunions" class="text-[13px] font-medium text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition">Lire l&rsquo;article</a>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="section-title mb-6 text-center">Ils parlent de nous</h2>
      <p class="body-text text-center mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Quelques articles de presse &agrave; propos de l&rsquo;Association Philat&eacute;lique de Valence.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2026/06/17/ce-n-est-pas-qu-un-truc-de-vieux-l-association-philatelique-a-100-ans" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">&laquo;&nbsp;Ce n&rsquo;est pas qu&rsquo;un truc de vieux.&nbsp;&raquo; L&rsquo;association philat&eacute;lique a 100 ans</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2026/03/07/la-86-sup-e-sup-fete-du-timbre-se-poursuit" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">La 86e f&ecirc;te du timbre se poursuit</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2025/09/08/forum-des-associations-de-valence-organise-par-association-philatelique-de-valence-gpso" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">Forum des associations de Valence organis&eacute; par l&rsquo;APV</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2025/03/08/la-fete-du-timbre-se-poursuit-dimanche" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">La f&ecirc;te du timbre se poursuit dimanche</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2025/02/21/philippe-stein-s-apprete-a-prendre-la-tete-de-l-association-philatelique" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">Philippe Stein s&rsquo;appr&ecirc;te &agrave; prendre la t&ecirc;te de l&rsquo;association philat&eacute;lique</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2023/09/17/la-maison-des-tetes-s-affiche-sur-carte-postale" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">La Maison des t&ecirc;tes s&rsquo;affiche sur carte postale</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2020/10/03/la-fete-du-timbre-a-84-ans" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block perforated p-5 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <p class="label">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute;</p>
          <p class="text-[15px] text-stone-800 font-medium">La f&ecirc;te du timbre a 84 ans</p>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>